#
Fonctionnalité / Besoin IA
Description
Type d’intelligence recommandé
1
Incident Summarization
Provide agents with a summarization of incident notes and history
LLM agentique (synthèse et contextualisation du langage naturel)
2
Incident Resolution Notes Generation
Reduce agents’ “wrap time” by generating accurate resolution notes based on actions taken and solution achieved. Reduce troubleshooting time as future agents can easily reference past incidents.
LLM agentique (génération de texte structurée à partir de logs et notes)
3
Knowledge Article Generation
Auto-generate draft knowledge articles via conversational experience based on incident records. Deflect future incidents with improved, comprehensive knowledge articles for employee end users.
LLM agentique (génération de contenu rédigé et contextualisé)
4
Investigate IT problems
Assist agent in identifying the root cause of a problem, assessing its impact and risks, and providing a clear and actionable resolution plan.
Hybride LLM + Graph reasoning / GNN (analyse de causes racines et corrélations topologiques)
5
Investigate and resolve ITSM incidents BNPP customization
Provides recommendations for a resolution using catalog, knowledge, changes, and past incidents and sends the information to the agent.
LLM + moteur de règles ou ML supervisé (recommandation guidée par historique et base de connaissance)
6
Triager and categorize ITSM incidents BNPP customization
Enables agents to determine the category, subcategory, and configuration item automatically for a given incident. After categorizing, it looks for related major incidents or known problems and links them automatically. Ask for agent approval before updating.
ML supervisé ou deep learning (classification NLP et similarité)
7
Analyze incident trends BNPP customization
Retrieve incident clusters, analyze data, identify recurring issues and root causes, and provide actionable recommendations. Provide the list of incidents for each cluster.
ML non supervisé ou GNN (clustering et détection de patterns récurrents)
8
Generate the PIR (Delivered by ISPL)
Reduce incident manager “wrap time” by generating a draft of PIR via conversational experience based on incident details.
LLM agentique (génération de rapport synthétique et conversationnel)
9
Activate OOTB recommended actions
Agents can quickly check related search results or similar records and perform AI-suggested actions (linking parent/child, copying notes, etc.).
Moteur de règles + ML de similarité (détection de similarité et déclenchement automatique)
10
Activate recommended prediction of fields
Agents can choose a recommended value when they need to set the Service or the CI for an incident. Suggested value is derived from historical data based on same entity and description.
ML supervisé ou deep learning tabulaire (prédiction de champs à partir du contexte et de l’historique)
11
Small adjustments on predictive / task intelligence models
Improve calculation of similarity or timing based on new criteria.
Optimisation de modèles ML existants (réglage d’hyperparamètres ou pondération)
12
Custom recommended action to link incidents as children
Provides agents with the possibility to group and link similar incidents into child/parent hierarchies.
GNN ou ML de corrélation (détection de liens topologiques dans le graphe d’incidents)
13
Setup of experts on-call feature (not configured)
Service desk managers can define on-call shifts and agents can contact experts directly for resolution of complex incidents.
LLM agentique + moteur de règles (orchestration contextuelle et suggestion d’experts)
14
Setup of email template
Agents can quickly compose new emails from predefined templates. Templates can be personalized by Entity.
LLM léger ou moteur de template (rédaction automatique guidée)
15
Setup of announcements
Agents can quickly see highlighted P1/P2 incidents to be aware of ongoing critical events.
Moteur de règles ou logique événementielle (notification automatique selon criticité)
16
Enhance the workspace with BNPP fields
The custom fields created by BNPP have been added to the Service Operations Workspace to give them an equivalent experience.
Aucune IA spécifique (configuration UI / modèle de données)
